                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">他虽具有大无畏的精神，但缺乏真正革命家所特有的冷酷。——这就是本书“勉为其难”的含义，可见其并非贬义，而是意图塑造孙中山过于理想化却又因此更显得纯粹的人格形象。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="770735645">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-770735645" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-770735645" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="770735645">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/HanDoudou/">σ ゜</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-01-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">滚下神坛</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="708989450">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-708989450" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-708989450" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="708989450">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bigeyedog/">大眼狗</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-07-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">作者虽然声称勉为其难之意是孙不愿充当革命者通常要做的残酷无情的角色，但我认为勉为其难的本意更适合评价孙中山，对于领导中国的社会革命，孙中山的人格和能力都力所不逮。话说回来，正是这些勉为其难的革命者们才能最后成为坐寇，这是中国历史的特色还是吊诡呢？</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="575950853">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-575950853" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-575950853" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="575950853">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/45706324/">wyongt</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-09-02</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">“国父”去神化</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="533598818">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-533598818" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-533598818" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="533598818">有用</a>
